,Recommended,277460,9789586,"Posted: 11 April, 2014",all,paul-w,"EDIT: Some compatibility issues, that are seemingly easy to fix;-Find 'Praetorians.exe' in the steam folder (Program Files, Steam, Steamapps, common, Praetorians)-Right click on it and select properties-Go to the 'Compatibility' tab-Select Run this program in compatibility mode, and select your operating system from the menuI'm running Windows 7, and this seems to have fixed the crashing problems when trying to start a game. Thanks to 'The Amazing SparKo' for his advice!ORIGINAL:A great game from years gone by, however this version is not working. The game will crash when I try to start any mission.Will update if the issue is fixed."
